<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 4. Labels. i Bulimus altoperuvianus Reeve, 1849 ii Bulimus amandus Pfeiffer, 1855 iii Bulimus ambustus Reeve, 1849 iv Bulimus andicola Pfeiffer, 1847 v Bulimus andoicus Morelet, 1863 vi Drymaeus angustus da Costa, 1906." , "Figure 56. Neopetraeus species. A-C Neopetraeus altoperuvianus (Reeve, 1849), lectotype NHMUK 1975437 (H = 46.5) D-F Neopetraeus atahualpa (Dohrn, 1863), possible syntype NHMUK 1975436 (H = 38.5) G-I Neopetraeus decussatus (Reeve, 1849), lectotype NHMUK 1975180 (H = 37.7) J-L Neopetraeus patasensis (Pfeiffer, 1858), lectotype NHMUK 1975439 (H = 46.8). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26755" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26728" .

